column2: SELECT Q.BestObjID, S.u, S.g, S.ra, S.dec, Q.z, G.ObjID, G.ra, G.dec, P.z, G.u, G.g, G.r, G.i, G.z, N.distance  From    Galaxy   as G, 		   SpecObj       as Q, 		   Neighbors       as N,		   SpecObj         as S,   Photoz          as P 		 WHERE Q.BestObjID = S.BestObjID 		   and S.z > #   and S.z < #   and S.u < #   and S.g <#   and G.g>#   and G.ObjID = P.ObjID   and P.z BETWEEN # and #   and photoErrorClass=#   and S.z>P.z   and Q.class  in (&&&, &&&) 	   and G.ObjID = N.ObjID		   and Q.BestObjID = N.NeighborObjID  	   and N.distance < #/#
